Download Mosquito Alert report data from GitHub

Source: R/get_malert_data.R
get_malert_data.Rd

Download Mosquito Alert report data from GitHub

Usage

get_malert_data(source = "github")

Arguments

source

String. Source to download from. Currently only github works.

Value

A tibble.

Examples

malert_reports = get_malert_data(source = "github")
#> [1] 2014
